Hello everyone,

This is my second map I've made,  My first (bad)map was: "bhop_chervona" .

Only the bonus of my map is made by pcpie. I wanted to make a bonus by myself, but pcpie had one for me which he wasn't planned to use anyways.

The map is between 40-50 seconds long and the bonus 7-9 seconds, something like that.

I hope you guys will enjoy the map :)
